    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事发生在某个闷热的夏季......</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/30117a73cdac4cc95dc567042c8f18db.poster.avif?t=1753575307\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/30117a73cdac4cc95dc567042c8f18db.webm?t=1753575307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/30117a73cdac4cc95dc567042c8f18db.mp4?t=1753575307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >投送包裹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骑着越野自行车在游戏的四个小镇里穿梭，将信件和包裹投递给个性稀奇古怪的小镇居民们。这些包裹大小不一，重量和形状也都五花八门，所以出发前记得规划好投递路线哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/05a5a27bfc98e036af3f4ed9cb72b4de.poster.avif?t=1753575307\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/05a5a27bfc98e036af3f4ed9cb72b4de.webm?t=1753575307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参加活动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你与镇民们日渐亲近，他们会邀请你去参加各种各样的活动。积极参加活动，就能获得形形色色的物品和奖励，帮助你重建神社。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/2683ebcc94bcbcba891174266421190d.poster.avif?t=1753575307\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/2683ebcc94bcbcba891174266421190d.webm?t=1753575307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >翻修神社</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用工作和参加活动赚来的资金和物品建造、升级并装饰神社，让它重现往日的风采，迎接夏末的庆典！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/2400619723735826d61829050ad18cf7.poster.avif?t=1753575307\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/2400619723735826d61829050ad18cf7.webm?t=1753575307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四大城镇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中共有四个主要城镇，分别融入了京都、青森、札幌和别府等四个城市的独特风格。每个小镇都有各自专属的任务和目标等待你去完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/15f8e3c6c8f9473f61c2b4200cff12de.poster.avif?t=1753575307\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218570/extras/15f8e3c6c8f9473f61c2b4200cff12de.webm?t=1753575307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >临近狸猫庆典，阿蓬不得不为了重建神社而东奔西走。快来帮他筹集经费、结识镇民、整饬神社，迎接一场此生难忘的盛大庆典吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身狸猫邮差骑着越野自行车闯入小镇居民的心房！你必须在一个月内整修好神社，顺利举办盛大的狸猫庆典。送包裹、打比赛、捏寿司……更多好玩活动，尽在胖哒的夏日！</p>",
